an arrangement.\n\nThere are 74 prisons in 72 districts of the country.\n\nThe committee had already recommended the home ministry to keep inmates in open jail and parole, form parole boards and make separate clusters of inmates based on their health status in a bid to allay virus transmission risk.","title":"Parliamentary committee directs govt to maintain standards in prison health - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/01/124205/","video":[]}
